      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "RPG Monster Generator + ControlNet + HiRes Fix Workflow\n\n[Setup - dependencies]\n1. Place a dungeon reference image at: ComfyUI/input/dungeon_ref_NN.png\n2. Download ControlNet model (Canny or Depth SDXL) -> ComfyUI/models/controlnet/\n3. Download 4x-UltraSharp.pth -> ComfyUI/models/upscale_models/\n4. Install via ComfyUI Manager:\n   - ComfyUI's ControlNet Auxiliary Preprocessors (Fannovel16)\n   - rgthree-comfy (for Seed and Image Comparer nodes)\n\n[Defaults]\n- Model: dreamshaperXL_lightningDPMSDE.safetensors (Tier 1)\n- RPG node offsets: 0 / 0 (STYLE_DATA defaults are tuned for Lightning)\n- Pass 1 KSampler (node 8): 8 steps / 2.0 cfg / dpmpp_sde / karras / denoise 1.0 (initial)\n- Pass 2 KSampler (node 20): 1 step / 2 cfg / dpmpp_sde / karras / denoise 0.45 (HiRes Fix)\n\n[ControlNet tuning - node 6]\n- strength: 0.45-0.65 (current 0.6, lower = more freedom)\n- end_percent: 0.5-0.7 (current 0.65, let creature dominate later)\n\n[Pipeline]\nLoadImage -> MiDaS Depth -> Apply ControlNet -> Pass 1 KSampler (1024x1024)\n-> Upscale 4x -> Resize/Pad 1536x1536 -> VAEEncode -> Pass 2 KSampler (denoise 0.45)\n-> SaveImage (yyyyMMdd_filename_prefix)\n\nImage Comparer shows Pass 1 vs Pass 2 side by side."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
